ZH: 我需要一个文具盒来放我的笔。
EN: I need a pencil case to hold my pens.

ZH: 这家店里有各种各样的文具供选择。
EN: There are a variety of stationery items to choose from in this store.

ZH: 我的书包里常常装满了文具。
EN: My backpack is often filled with stationery.

ZH: 她总是在课间时间购买新的文具。
EN: She always buys new stationery during break time.

ZH: 这本笔记本上面有很多有趣的文具图案。
EN: This notebook has many interesting stationery designs on it.

ZH: 他收集了很多不同种类的文具。
EN: He collects a lot of different types of stationery.

ZH: 我的文具太乱了，找不到我要的东西了。
EN: My stationery is too messy, I can't find what I need.

ZH: 这里有一个文具店，你可以在那里买到你需要的一切。
EN: There is a stationery store here where you can buy everything you need.

ZH: 我在文具店里买了一根新的铅笔。
EN: I bought a new pencil at the stationery store.

ZH: 这个文具盒可以容纳很多笔和铅笔。
EN: This pencil case can hold a lot of pens and pencils.

ZH: 我用这支笔从文具盒里写下了我的笔记。
EN: I used this pen from the pencil case to write down my notes.

